	<text>The burnt out hull of a Rock Trapper drifts by. Behind the wreck drifts a live mine; an automated drone that drills into ships' hulls before exploding. However, it can't detect you from this range, and you wonder if it's even active. Still, it's risky...</text>
	<choice hidden="true">
