			</choice>
			<choice hidden="true" req="BLUELIST_ARMOR">
				<text>(Armor Plating) Your armor will protect you.</text>
				<event>
					<text>The mine struggles to even burrow into your ship. Its drill eventually runs out of power and drifts away, now rendered harmless.</text>
