<event name="ROCK_ASTEROID_COLONY_PIRATE" unique="true">
	<text>The pirate vessel crashes down into the ground, but luckily the civilians are unharmed. No one protests as you salvage the wreckage of the pirate ship.</text>
	<autoReward level="MED">standard</autoReward>
	<choice hidden="true">
		<text>Contact the civilians.</text>
