<event name="ROCK_ZOLTAN_PARASITE" unique="true">
	<text>A Rock station nearby is mass-broadcasting a request for medical aid. "Medical assistance required at Station R-0735Q. Need help extracting parasite. Will pay."</text>
	<distressBeacon/>
	<choice hidden="true">
		<text>Offer to help.</text>
		<event>
			<text>The Rockmen are mildly confused that a Federation ship is offering to help, but don't complain. "We are representatives for Zulfiqar Industries. Yesterday, CMO Rig Bramston arranged a meeting on these premisces with a Zoltan envoy named Tintan to discuss means of distribution and marketing within the Ministry. However, we did not anticipate a Slug vessel to arrive shortly after and deploy a 'prank' on the meeting, mind controlling Rig to consume Tintan whole. As you can understand, we are now in quite the dilemma and need to operate immediately."</text>
			<choice hidden="true">
				<text>Suggest they simply put them out of their collective misery.</text>
				<event>
					<text>"Your advice is worthless. We cannot simply assasinate both a high ranking Zoltan official and our own commander. We ask that you leave, and we will wait for a more helpful ship to arrive."</text>
				</event>
			</choice>
			<choice hidden="true">
				<text>Offer to try and perform surgery.</text>
				<event>
					<text>"Do you have any training in operating of either of the two species? Or any species at all?" You shake your head. "Then get lost. We will wait for someone who knows what they are doing to arrive."</text>
				</event>
			</choice>
			<choice hidden="true" req="mind">
				<text>(Mind Control) Convince the two to live in symbiosis aboard your ship.</text>
				<event>
					<text>Even under the effects of the mind control, it takes a lot of convincing to get the two to agree with forever existing among one another. Their life forever changed, now remarkably for the better, they thank you, and even ask to join your crew. The Rock station is confused as to what has happened, but Rig seems certain this is the right option in his stupor and the Rockmen agree to let him go.</text>
					<autoReward level="MED">standard</autoReward>
					<crewMember amount="1" all_skills="1" class="symbiote">Tintan and Rig</crewMember>
					<hiddenAug>ACH_CREW_SYMBIOTE</hiddenAug>
				</event>
			</choice>
			<choice hidden="true" req="LIST_CREW_MANTIS">
				<text>(Mantis Crew) Perform "surgery" on the Rockman.</text>
				<event>
					<text>Your Mantis, ever assured of its abilities, pushes past the Rockmen and marches into the room where the "infected" Rockman is being held. In a single swipe, it cuts straight through the stomach. The convulsing Zoltan falls out, quivering on the ground. The makeshift Rock medical team rushes in to fix the injured Rockman and physiologically evaluate the Zoltan. They aren't pleased with your solution, but they pay you as promised anyways.</text>
					<autoReward level="LOW">standard</autoReward>
				</event>
			</choice>
			<choice hidden="true" req="tonysr">
				<text>(Tony Sr.) Rig, is that you?</text>
				<event>
					<text>"My god... Tony? Is that you? How are you here?" You have no idea what's going on, but Tony explains. "7 years ago Tony's was nothing but a small chain local only to the Republic and quite small. I hoped to change that around by selling Zulfiqar goods. I met with Rig to discuss the terms when out of nowhere a Slug ship arrived and mind controlled me into sticking myself up Rig's... uh... asshole. The surgeons had no idea how to handle the situation. For 3 years we lived like that, stuck together. I was forced to eat Rig's waste to survive. Eventually we found a professional capable of separating us, but it was too late to save either of us from the permanent trauma."</text>
					<choice hidden="true">
						<text>Uh...</text>
						<event>
							<text>The Rock station owners are completely baffled as to what is happening, but together you, Tony, Rig, and Tintan discuss the situation. It becomes clear Rig and Tintan won't be free of each other any time soon, but with Tony's help you might just be able to track down the Slugs responsible and get revenge.</text>
							<hiddenAug>ACH_CREW_SYMBIOTE</hiddenAug>
							<crewMember all_skills="1" amount="1" class="symbiote">Tintan and Rig</crewMember>
							<quest event="BUTT_BUDDIES"/>
						</event>
					</choice>
				</event>
			</choice>
		</event>
	</choice>
	<choice hidden="true">
		<text>We cannot help.</text>
		<event>
			<text>You ignore the Rock station and carry on your way.</text>
			<choice>
				<text>Do something onboard the ship.</text>
				<event load="STORAGE_CHECK"/>
			</choice>
			<choice>
				<text>Do nothing.</text>
