			<text>"Tuco and the other escapees overwhelmed the slavers and escaped by stealing a Hephaestus-built vessel. Tuco gained infamy among pirates and Theocracy citizens alike. He returned to the Badlands, and together with the forces of Admiral Ariadne of the Lost Sun fleet drove Tiiikaka from the Badlands once again. Tuco stayed with us Outcasts for some time until he grew restless, and once again departed to seek greater adventures in the starry beyond!"</text>
