<textList name="TEXT_OUTCAST_SLAVER">
	<text>"Pssssst... pssssst... hey, over here. I got somethin' that might interest you. And no, it's not drugs. Don't ask me, I don't got any. I'm in the slave business, drugs are just bad for your health." You aren't sure why he's so worked up over this, but true to his word he appears to be offering slaves for 'cheap'.</text>
	<text>No surprise to find a Tiiikaka vessel out here, but you are shocked when they immediately approach and offer you a slave! These pirates are getting bolder every day. Or dumber. Probably dumber, to be honest.</text>
</textList>

