<textList name="TEXT_ENCOUNTER_OUTCAST">
	<text>When Rockmen go against the Elders, there is not much left for them to become other than outcast pirates or refugees without a future. One such ship patrols the nearby system, and upon spotting you decide your ship would make an excellent target for them!</text>
	<text>A ship full of Rock outcasts sees you first. Apparently they are no longer satisfied with the condition of their vessel, because now they're looking to take yours instead.</text>
	<text>Outcasts are refugees from the Rock Government. Now forced to live the life of a pirate, they have no choice but to prey on ships such as yours to survive.</text>
</textList>

<event name="ENCOUNTER_SSLG">
	<text load="TEXT_ENCOUNTER_SSLG"/>
