	<text>You've arrived at the destination Ruwen provided you with. Moments later, the Crystal arrives, jubilant as ever. "We meet again! You have my thanks, captain! As promised, your reward. Now, if you don't mind, I must hurry to my meeting. Idi Tukala! Erm, sorry. That's... that's goodbye in my native language. Apologies."</text>
	<autoReward level="MED">scrap_only</autoReward>
