			<text>It seems Ruwen's substantial defenses protected him from any major damage during the fight. Still, he's quite shaken. "By the Empress, oh dear. Had it not been for you I doubt I would still be standing here. It would be against tradition for me to not extend an even greater reward as thanks to you and the Federation. Though my initial diplomatic mission here has failed, perhaps we have achieved new ground instead!"</text>
