					<text>"Now, erm, it seems there's little point in keeping past pretenses so let me begin again. I needn't waste your time which much historical mumble, but in short the Empire has been so tollerant of the SSLG's more radical motions as the Empress sees great benefit in gaining access to Theocracy grounds. We seek access to the Waystone, the device originally used to seal our homeworlds away from the galaxy. At first, we hoped the Lost Suns might retrieve it for us in return for more dedicated support. But now it seems those plans have faltered. Now, I must go at it alone. It will be perilous, but I wonder if you might be up for the task?"</text>
